verbose_text: In this study, we focused on patients simultaneously diagnosed with OB/T2D, in order to determine BRS-3 expression levels in skeletal muscle sections and to assess the effects of the BRS-3 agonist, [D-Tyr 6 -beta-Ala 11, Phe 13, Nle 14] bombesin 6-14, on glucose related processes in primary cultured myocytes.
